## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Ubuntu 20.04+ (local VM or AWS EC2)
- AWS account with EC2 access
- OpenVAS / Greenbone Community Edition

### Run the hardening script

```bash
git clone https://github.com/harsh301002/linux-cloud-hardening.git
cd linux-cloud-hardening/scripts

chmod +x harden_linux.sh
sudo ./harden_linux.sh
```

### Verify hardening applied

```bash
sudo ./audit_check.sh
```

